OL,3,C'Where do families go?' Crisis facing
OL,4,CChildren's Hospice
OL,6,FThe mother of a young boy who uses the
OL,7,FChildren's Hospice has spoken of how
OL,8,Fvital the service is to her and her
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,FIt comes as the Glengormley-based
OL,12,Fcharity is in a funding crisis and
OL,13,Fhaving to reduce the number of beds it
OL,14,Fcan facilitate.
OL,16,FOisin McConnell has complex medical
OL,17,Fneeds needing 24-hour care. The 13-
OL,18,Fyear-old has been attending the centre
OL,19,Fsince he was three.
