OL,3,C'Where do families go?' Crisis facing
OL,4,CChildren's Hospice
OL,6,F"If we want to plan something as a
OL,7,Ffamily, if we want to go out, even if
OL,8,Fwe want some sleep, it is vital to
OL,9,Fus," his mother Natalie told UTV.
OL,11,FThey usually get three or four nights
OL,12,Fcare from the hospice, but with
OL,13,Fpressures on the beds that will now be
OL,14,Ftwo nights at most.
OL,16,F"You are going to have families coming
OL,17,Fthrough needing to access this service
OL,18,Fwho maybe aren't going to access this
OL,19,Fservice.
OL,21,F"Where do they turn?
