OL,3,C'Where do families go?' Crisis facing
OL,4,CChildren's Hospice
OL,6,F"There is nothing else like it for
OL,7,Fthis diagnosis, for these type of
OL,8,Fchildren."
OL,10,FThe Health Minister has asked his
OL,11,Fofficials to engage with the Northern
OL,12,FIreland's Children Hospice to try and
OL,13,F"determine the best way forward" by
OL,14,Fthe end of this week.
OL,16,FThe charity said it deeply regretted
OL,17,Fthe move to cut services but it would
OL,18,Fhelp ensure long-term sustainability.
